{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0de4644d2","title":"中共中央关于皖北区党委对阜阳水灾处理措施给华东局的复电","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7653a4ceb2","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":12,"articleId":"c0de4644d2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"53456241d6","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于皖北区党委对阜阳水灾处理措施给华东局的复电","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"94c6b7c360","type":"appellation","text":"华东局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"79d9db0a7f","type":"paragraph","text":"午齐电悉。皖北区党委对阜阳水灾所决定的五项措施尚属妥当，你们意见如何?如同意，即复电准照办。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"6fe7bbb228","type":"paragraph","text":"又霍邱南堤溃决，淹死七十余人，应电各防汛区今后对抢救人命特别注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"7bba5b30e9","type":"paragraph","text":" 中 央午 文","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"f7e9b4a189","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"62b9926f95","type":"subtitle","text":"华东局转报皖北区党委关于阜阳水灾处理意见的电报","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"9d612d4b4d","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五O年七月八日）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"3a9a82f561","type":"appellation","text":"中央","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"7dd1e83b4b","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将皖北区党委午虞电转上：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"9f07d3b157","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局并曾、黄 [曾希圣、黄岩 --编者] 并阜阳地委：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"89f52338f5","type":"paragraph","text":"据报阜阳专区有一百五十个乡遭水灾，平地水深丈余，房舍庄稼全部淹没，水势尚在上涨。我们决定：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"21ba3ef72b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）即由交通处派轮船五只，拖带大批民船，前去受灾地区抢救灾民。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"1b1e95cee6","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）由华东原批准之救济粮中，拨杂粮五百万斤作急救之用。另，由东北贷粮中即拨五百万斤贷给灾区，兑换晚秋种子。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"1f0cc9f241","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）行署郑副主任[指郑抱真--编者]并携带医疗队即往阜阳，指示并布置抢救工作。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"d594b23925","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）阜阳参加整风干部全部回去，抢救灾民及防","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"79ee05ed54","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）当即于今晚召集沿淮、沿江各分区负责同志，对防汛工作作通盘研究，分别作紧急指示，提高警惕，加强对防汛工作的检查与领导，以确保安全。以上布置有何指示，请即电告。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"},{"id":"bb5c6b72b9","type":"paragraph","text":" 华东局午  齐","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2"}],"page":{"id":"a3fbff1466","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c0de4644d2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}